term: Party / Country views on Jay's Treaty
content:
federalists would be thrilled since the us stayed out of war
DRs would be angry because they went and didn’t get what they came for
	this treaty wasn’t much different from the one at the end of the American Revolution
	it was like we resigned we already signed

the DRs mocked this treaty, but it did get passed since the federalists were in control of the senate at this time
